// Default icon at ID 1 -- this is the ID BuildAndPatch.java overwrites in
// Step 3. default.ico is bundled with this tutorial (a plain blue icon)
// so target.exe is fully self-contained and builds without you needing to
// supply anything -- the same idea as compiling a placeholder icon into a
// native launcher stub before a user ever picks their own custom icon.
1 ICON "default.ico"
